    </p>

    <div class="flex justify-end gap-3">
      <button
        onclick="document.getElementById('modal-excluir-registro').classList.add('hidden')"
        class="px-4 py-2 bg-gray-200 text-gray-800 rounded hover:bg-gray-300"
      >
        Cancelar
